    <item>
      <title>中国疾病控制中心发现新型 Mpox 毒株群</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/china-disease-control-agency-detects-cluster-of-new-mpox-strain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自世界卫生组织去年宣布非洲疫情为新的全球卫生紧急事件以来，中国又发现了猪痘病毒的新变异毒株，该病原体已传播至更多地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/china-disease-control-agency-detects-cluster-of-new-mpox-strain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 04:03:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国重点打击金融、能源腐败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/china-singles-out-finance-energy-in-anti-graft-fight-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国结束了为期三天的反腐大会，承诺将在金融、能源和体育等多个行业加大反腐力度。反腐行动是国家媒体关注的焦点，中央电视台正在播出有关反腐的纪录片系列。彭博社的 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/china-singles-out-finance-energy-in-anti-graft-fight-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:44:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国如何应对通货紧缩压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/what-china-can-do-to-tackle-deflationary-pressures-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国消费者通胀连续第四个月放缓，随着通货紧缩压力持续存在，通胀进一步向零靠拢。法国农业信贷银行首席中国经济学家智晓佳表示，政策制定者需要在 2025 年“采取更多行动”来推动通胀再膨胀。她与 David Ingles 和 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 在“彭博：中国秀”节目中进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/what-china-can-do-to-tackle-deflationary-pressures-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称欧盟外商补贴法构成贸易壁垒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/china-says-eu-s-foreign-subsidies-law-amounts-to-trade-barrier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，欧盟为保护中国企业免受外国补贴而采取的措施是对贸易和投资的阻碍，这是双方持续贸易争端的最新冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/china-says-eu-s-foreign-subsidies-law-amounts-to-trade-barrier</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
